headline.main: LETTERS FROM KANSAS.; The Cities of Kansas.

docs.lead_paragraph: The cities of Kansas have been spoken of through the press and otherwise, to an extent which has produced considerable misapprehension. Some of them have been advertised with an energy and facility of statement which would do honor to the palmy days of 1835, and all have been, at different times, represented as favored spots where the adventurous have but to locate and moderately invest,

headline.main: EUROPEAN AFFAIRS.; Doings of the Vienna Conference-What is Doing in the Crimea,

docs.lead_paragraph: The "Congress of Vienna," launched on the 14th of Mfarch, is already on the high sea of diplomacy. That it is bound for the Pacific Ocean of protocols, treaties, and such other monsters, we all know, but where it will arrive at nobody knows. The log-book is to be kept from public sight, and people on board are warned not to speal to " the men at the wheel." Secrecy is to be the watch.
